item.title: Sky - By TheAtomicMixers [Collab?]
item.dc:creator: akabillposters
item.description:
You will also be able to repost this on your soundcloud and post it on your YouTube with at the end of the title saying: ft. TheAtomicMixers

Fwiw, it’s very unusual* to have the same track with two (or more) different titles or credit formats.

(* I’ve never heard of it happening)

I recommend agreeing on who’s the main artist and who’s the featured artist, or whether you opt for a straight collab (equal billing – e.g. TheAtomicMixers & [Second Artist] - [Track name]

That way, listeners understand the track better and it makes better sense from an ISRC perspective if the track is ever formally released.
